okay just leaving this out here for anyone interested;
if you can't hear any dialog and you don't want to mess around with ffdshow's mixer matrix everytime you play the movie here's what you gotta do.. extract the raw aac stream with YAMB,export to a multichannel wave with FAAD,downmix that using WaveWizard,transcode the resulting wave file to whatever format you like and mux it back (MegUI has all the tools you need).
or you can just play it with WMP lol
